name: Mochi Shooter 2000
description:
You are a my bunny Mochi and a lot of cabbage is falling on you so you poop on it to survive(●'◡'●) 

When you destroy a cabbage you get more damage.

If you touch a cabbage you die.

The cabbages get stronger with time...
